    <div class="container">
        <h1>About Fetch Labs</h1>
        <p><strong>Fetch Labs LLC</strong> is a research and development startup dedicated to pioneering innovative solutions at the intersection of media, technology, and community engagement. Founded in 2025 by <a href="about-ceo.html">David Drebes</a>, Fetch Labs explores novel ways to leverage contemporary technologies in unique combinations, delivering impactful products and services.</p>

        <h2>Our Focus Areas</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Media & Innovation:</strong> Providing cutting-edge services to media companies, including <a href="polling.html">non-partisan polling</a> and data-driven insights.</li>
            <li><strong>Automated Information Collection:</strong> Developing tools that curate and personalize information for consumers.</li>
            <li><strong>Digital Entertainment:</strong> Creating and distributing fresh, engaging digital entertainment products.</li>
            <li><strong>Community & Non-Profits:</strong> Researching hyper-local information-sharing and community-building strategies for nonprofit organizations.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Fetch Labs is incorporated in <strong>Missouri</strong>, and its official filing with the Secretary of State can be viewed <a href="https://bsd.sos.mo.gov/Common/CorrespondenceItemViewHandler.ashx?IsTIFF=true&filedDocumentid=137994041&version=2" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>

        <p>Our main laboratory is based in <strong>St. Louis, Missouri</strong>, with a satellite laboratory at <strong>Pine Tree Lake in Potosi, Missouri</strong>.</p>

